{"tid":934817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母親車禍喪命 獨居女留遺書燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-12-09T14:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T14:33:21.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2722dbe95b50407b6b5ec9fcc2d4e5472a09db26","tid":934817,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"深水埗發生燒炭自殺案！傍晚6時許，警方接獲一名女子報案，指其44歲的女親友倒卧在九江街一單位內。警員接報到場，經救護員檢驗證實女事主已氣絕身亡，她身旁有一盤燒過的炭。警方在單位內撿獲一封遺書，初步相信事件沒有可疑。<br />\n消息指，女事主的母親在今年一宗車禍中喪命，自此她鬱鬱不歡，更曾向身邊朋友透露不開心。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=es%2BtSAvE9Ha4YFt1qxhR2Rxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=1270d45f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181209/59011236\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59011236&d=es%2BtSAvE9Ha4YFt1qxhR2Rxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=59fe86e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59011236&h=c60162a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181209/59011236</a>"}]}